---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — StackSwitch"
  description="How StackSwitch collects, uses, and protects your data. We use minimal tracking and respect your GDPR rights."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-10">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Who we are</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          StackSwitch is an independent SaaS comparison website operated from the United Kingdom.
          When we say "we", "us", or "our" in this policy, we mean StackSwitch.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">What data we collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">We collect very little personal data. Specifically:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> If you use our contact form, we collect your name, email address, and message content. This is processed via StaticForms.</li>
          <li><strong>Email sign-ups:</strong> If you subscribe to our mailing list, we collect your name and email address.</li>
          <li><strong>Basic analytics:</strong> We may use privacy-respecting analytics to understand page views and general usage patterns. We do not use invasive tracking tools.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> See the Cookies section below.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          We do not collect payment information, passwords, or sensitive personal data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">How we use your data</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">We use the data we collect to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Respond to enquiries submitted through our contact form</li>
          <li>Send comparison reports and updates to subscribers who have opted in</li>
          <li>Understand which pages and tools are most useful, so we can improve the site</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          StackSwitch uses minimal cookies:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Cookie consent preference:</strong> We store your cookie consent choice in local storage so we do not ask you repeatedly.</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> If analytics are enabled, a small number of cookies may be set to measure page views. These do not identify you personally.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          We do not use advertising cookies, retargeting pixels, or social media trackers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Your rights under GDPR</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          As a UK/EU resident, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Right of access:</strong> You can request a copy of any personal data we hold about you.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to rectification:</strong> You can ask us to correct inaccurate data.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to erasure:</strong> You can ask us to delete your data.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to restrict processing:</strong> You can ask us to limit how we use your data.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to data portability:</strong> You can request your data in a machine-readable format.</li>
          <li><strong>Right to object:</strong> You can object to processing based on legitimate interests.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          To exercise any of these rights, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@stackswitch.co" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">hello@stackswitch.co</a>.
          We will respond within 30 days.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We use the following third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 mt-3">
          <li><strong>StaticForms</strong> — for processing contact form submissions</li>
          <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — for hosting the website</li>
          <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — for loading the Inter typeface</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          Each of these services has their own privacy policy. We recommend reviewing them if you have concerns about how your data may be processed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Data retention</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We retain contact form submissions and subscriber data for as long as necessary to fulfil the purpose for which it was collected.
          You can request deletion at any time by emailing
          <a href="mailto:hello@stackswitch.co" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">hello@stackswitch.co</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          If you have questions about this privacy policy or your data, contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
          <a href="mailto:hello@stackswitch.co" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">hello@stackswitch.co</a>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

  </div>
</Base>
